modify_feature

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
modify_feature -  This method is used to modify the descriptions and/or item descs of an established feature.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs void modify_feature(string title,
string * descs,
mixed item_desc)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^title%^RESET%^ - the name of the feature
%^BOLD%^descs%^RESET%^ - array of descriptions to be shown at different ranges.
add_item name(s) (identical to the 'shorts' parameter in add_item)
%^BOLD%^item_desc%^RESET%^ - a string, or array of strings giving the corresponding
These are divided equally along the total range
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/terrain_map/handler_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is used to modify the descriptions and/or item descs of
an established feature. Changes will be instantly seen in all the
rooms the feature is visible from.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_feature_chats, add_feature, add_item

.EP

